"{\n  \"correct\": \"no\",\n  \"explanation\": \"The code incorrectly uses sns.set_context() with the rc argument to customize seaborn styles. According to the seaborn documentation, the rc argument should be used with sns.axes_style() or sns.set_style() to override style parameters. The sns.set_context() function is used to set the context parameters, not style parameters.\",\n  \"patch\": \"9c9\\n< sns.set_context(rc=viz_dict)\\n---\\n> sns.set_style(rc=viz_dict)\\n\"\n}"